			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4402498">
									

<p>SCP Illustrated brought me here and I have to say, this was a fantastic tale. It combined two of my favorite SCP’s into a relatively short but harrowing story that kept me enthralled throughout.</p>
<p>The idea that there are more underground safe havens in addition to UnLondon has a great amount of potential, and I can’t wait to see where you guys go in terms of exploring UnDublin. I’m also looking forward to reading the tales involving survivors utilizing other SCP’s to escape from the sun’s wrath.</p>
<p>Great job to everyone involved, and I can’t wait to see what else is in store for this storyline! +1</p>

